<section id="feature1">
    <h3>
        Share my institutional agreement information with others
    </h3>
    <p>
        <strong>In order to</strong> promote awareness of my organization's global academic
        engagement,
        <br />
        <strong>As an</strong> international office,
        <br />
        <strong>I want to</strong> share international agreement information with my students,
        employees, and the public.
    </p>
    <p>
        Hopefully you've noticed the new look and feel. This re-design does not apply to
        the entire system yet, but it is used in all publicly-accessible screens. Read on
        to the next feature for more on how we can apply your brand using this new layout.
    </p>
    <p>
        Up until now, those users who have been entering agreements have been dealing with
        administrative screens that are not publicly accessible. This preview contains the
        first release of an institutional agreements public view that you can begin linking
        to from your internal web pages. The search feature is the only missing piece, and
        it is planned for deployment next week.
    </p>
