    <p>
        When managing institutional agreement data, the following rules apply to the public
        view:
    </p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Public</strong> fields can be seen by anyone.</li>
        <li><strong>Protected</strong> fields can only be seen by someone who is signed in with
            an email address under your institution's control (for example, usr4@lehigh.edu).</li>
        <li><strong>Private</strong> fields can only be seen by specific designated users.</li>
    </ol>
